Class AlienHousing

java.lang.Object
org.mio.progettoingsoft.model.Component
org.mio.progettoingsoft.model.components.AlienHousing
public class AlienHousing extends Component
Represents an "Alien Housing" component on a spaceship. This component extends the base Component class and specifically holds an alien guest of a particular color.
